<PageTitle>B3 Components and Routing</PageTitle>

<h1>B3. Components, Layout, and Routing</h1>

<p>
	This sample focuses on route mapping and component composition patterns in a Blazor Web App.
</p>

<ul>
	<li><strong>Route Parameter</strong>: Demonstrates <code>@@page "/policy/{id:int}"</code> and parameter binding.</li>
	<li><strong>Multi Route</strong>: Demonstrates multiple route templates and optional route parameters.</li>
	<li><strong>Composition</strong>: Demonstrates Shared component parameter and <code>EventCallback</code> wiring.</li>
</ul>
